IN A NEW RELATIONSHIP NOW

15:43.609 --> 15:45.194
AND VERY HAPPY.

15:45.277 --> 15:46.862
ONWARDS AND UPWARDS, NO REGRETS.

15:46.945 --> 15:49.323
- OH, THERE'S ALWAYS REGRETS.

15:49.406 --> 15:51.992
I HAD A MAN,
MY FIRST LOVE, IN FACT.

15:52.076 --> 15:55.704
HE WAS HANDSOME
AND CRAGGY, QUITE A CATCH.

15:55.788 --> 16:00.417
BUT THEN I WAS CONSIDERED
A GREAT BEAUTY IN MY HOME TOWN.

16:00.501 --> 16:04.713
- WAS IT A SMALL TOWN?

16:04.797 --> 16:07.633
- IT WAS, BUT
I DIDN'T TREAT HIM WELL,

16:07.716 --> 16:09.218
AND I LOST HIM
TO ANOTHER WOMAN.

16:09.301 --> 16:11.929
YOU SAY YOU'RE HAPPY
WITH YOUR NEW MAN,

16:12.012 --> 16:14.390
BUT THERE MUST BE PART OF YOU

16:14.473 --> 16:16.684
THAT DREAMED
OF KEEPING YOUR CLAN TOGETHER.

16:16.767 --> 16:18.894
- I SUPPOSE SO.
- MM.

16:18.977 --> 16:20.771
JUST THINK OF THE CHRISTMASES.

16:20.854 --> 16:23.565
THE BAIRN AND HIS PARENTS
AND GRANDPARENTS

16:23.649 --> 16:25.609
